dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.[These data are intended for tax parcel mapping.]
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents parcels for Portage County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Portage_Parcels_2015.gdb. [The Parcel data set is a vector representation of tax parcel boundaries and associated parcel attributes in Portage County, Wisconsin. The parcels are created by using coordinate geometry and digitizing from digital orthophotography.
